        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for sending his article in the <hi rend="italic">Westminster Review</hi> [n.s. 41 (1872): 28–49] and the notice of CD’s work.</p> 
            <p>Natural selection is under a cloud at present, but CD expects that it will be resuscitated.</p>
